%% Deployment architecture (Mermaid)
flowchart LR
  User --> LB[Load Balancer / Ingress]
  LB --> IngressController[Ingress Controller / NGINX]
  IngressController --> FrontendSvc[Frontend Service (K8s)]
  IngressController --> BackendSvc[Backend Service (K8s)]
  BackendSvc --> PostgresDB[(Managed Postgres Cluster)]
  BackendSvc --> RedisCache[(Managed Redis / Memorystore)]
  BackendSvc --> MinIO[(Object Storage / Cloud Storage)]
  BackendSvc --> MessageBroker[(RabbitMQ / PubSub)]
  CI[CI/CD Pipeline] -->|deploy| K8sCluster[Kubernetes Cluster / Container Apps]
  K8sCluster --> Monitoring[(Prometheus / Grafana / Loki)]
  K8sCluster --> Logging[(ELK / Loki)]
